data.description: Priced under recent appraisal! Welcome home to this French Country one story offering a two year old roof and 4 bedrooms PLUS an office. The open floor plan offers great natural light and a spacious Living Room with a pretty fireplace. The office is located off the Breakfast room and bedrooms are a split plan. There are hard floors throughout most of the home. This Kitchen offers TWO pantries, breakfast bar, ample cabinetry, stainless appliances including gas cooking and freshly painted cabinetry. The Primary Bedrooms offers a tray ceiling and lavish bath with a spa tub and separate shower plus double walk in closets and double vanities. There is an attached oversized double garage and plenty of driveway space. The water heater has been replaced. Location can't be beat with easy access to I-12 and in a top school district.  A French door from the Breakfast room brings you to the covered patio overlooking the huge backyard which is fully fenced. Flood zone C so no flood insurance required plus a 2 year old roof and new water heater = reasonable insurance! Appraised May 2023 350k. See attached in MLS. This home is eligible for FHA, RD or VA loans. Take a look today and make it yours!
